org.openhubframework.openhub.spi.node

Interface ChangeNodeCallback

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NodeRpc.ChangeCallback

    public interface ChangeNodeCallback
    Callback function for update Node in NodeService.update(Node, ChangeNodeCallback). In method updateNode(MutableNode) we can change all node attributes.
    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Roman Havlicek
    See Also:
    NodeService.update(Node, ChangeNodeCallback), Node, MutableNode
